{"word":"G3038 - λιθόστρωτος - lithóstrōtos - lith-os'-tro-tos - Pavement","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λιθόστρωτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">lithóstrōtos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">lith-os'-tro-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pavement</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தள வரிசையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"spread (paved) with stones"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3037 - λίθος - líthos - lee'-thos/3037\">G3037</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4766 - στρώννυμι - strṓnnymi - strone'-noo-mee/4766\">G4766</a>; <i>stone strewed</i>, that is, a tessellated <i>mosaic</i> on which the Roman tribunal was placed: - Pavement.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3035/3035\">G3035</a>, <a href=\"#/G3037/3037\">G3037</a>, <a href=\"#/G3038/3038\">G3038</a>"}]}